{
  "stem": "4284.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so I was sitting in France.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, France didn't seem to be a future, not that I had enough sense to figure out what my future would be.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I had volunteered, one of the few times I did, to go on the exodus to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I wanted to get out of Europe.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was assigned to it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And two weeks before I was to leave, one of the newspapers had been seen by an uncle who lived in Los Angeles.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they made arrangement that I should come to come to the United States.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In, in April 20 of 1946.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was privileged to have the, sort of, opportunity to sit in a cafe.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, big shots, you know, kids were sitting in a cafe in Paris.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And since I did speak German and one other fellows from Lithuania spoke German-- he didn't pick Yiddish up very well-- a neighboring couple looked over.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they thought it was strange we have not yet grown our hair back.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was our first opportunity.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we, were were looking the little stubbles that were growing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "This was, of course, still in, in early '45-- I mean, middle '45, when I had already known that my family had found me in the newspaper and-- in, in the listing.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we were discussing, because I was very excited.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And this gentleman asked the waiter to bring me over.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he happened to be from Germany, Jewish, lives in France for a long time, was in the Ministry of Transportation.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I mean, the coincidence on a cafe encounter-- and he was able to provide me with the first ship to leave Europe with civilians on it after the war to come to the United States.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So I've been very lucky.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
